Class BulkOperationResponse

java.io.Serializable
public class BulkOperationResponse
extends BaseResponse

The HTTP response of all Bulk Operations (Create, Update, Delete) in SIF3 have certain structure. This class is an abstract representation response, so that developers don't need to know the low level infrastructure details of a Bulk Response. The Bulk Response returns a status or an error for each object in the original bulk request. This class is a list of the responses to each object in the original bulk request.

Author:
Joerg Huber
